700388f-a.title: Bronx: 261st Street (West) - Fieldston Road
700388f-a.text:
West 26lst Street, north side, east from Fieldston Road to Broadway
and Van Cortlandt Park. On the left appears Fieldston Road running north
to West 262nd Street.
About 1914.
James Suydam.
